## Data Flow

```mermaid
sequenceDiagram
    participant User
    participant Nginx
    participant StaticFiles
    participant FormService
    
    Note over User,Nginx: Static Site - No Server-Side Processing
    
    User->>Nginx: Request /portfolio
    Nginx->>StaticFiles: Serve static HTML
    StaticFiles-->>User: HTML + CSS + JS
    
    User->>Nginx: Request /blog/first-post
    Nginx->>StaticFiles: Serve blog post HTML
    StaticFiles-->>User: Blog article
    
    Note over User,FormService: Form Submission (Client-Side)
    
    User->>FormService: Submit contact form
    FormService-->>User: Success/Confirmation
    FormService->>You: Email notification
```

